  "nl": "Symmetry: If f̂ is invariant under swapping features i and j, then φ_i = φ_j",
  "formal": "∀ i, j: [∀ x: f̂(x|_{X_i=a, X_j=a}) = f̂(x|_{X_i=b, X_j=b}) ∀ a, b] ⇒ φ_i = φ_j",
